    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《计划II：寂静谷》属于“计划 Projects”系列世界观的一部分，但每一部作品均为<strong>独立叙事</strong>。本作不需要了解前作剧情，也不会影响游戏体验。你可以将其视为同一世界中，不同时间与地点发生的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287360/extras/c9be7debcb60db4df3f55853e24f392b.avif?t=1770501295\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287360/extras_big/c9be7debcb60db4df3f55853e24f392b.avif?t=1770501295 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《计划II：寂静谷》是一款融合视觉小说、卡牌战斗与世界探索的<strong>叙事游戏</strong>，讲述了温柔的海军中校埃尔凡·海默斯菲尔德与他的临时副官——特种作战人员鱼鹰，以及昔日挚友奥奇拉·布雷兹摩之间错综复杂的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287360/extras/d35c2f50c8a5b441e3e01819e30392bc.webp?t=1770501295\" width=263 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个反乌托邦的平行美国，&quot;无域财团(N.C.)&quot;已经颠覆了传统政府。如今的美国被两大势力瓜分：掌控主要区域的&quot;N.C.政府&quot;实行严酷的军事化管理，而&quot;旧政府&quot;作为原政权的残余势力割据一方。表面的和平共存之下，暗流涌动的权力斗争愈发激烈...在这个充斥着异化与集权的世界中，身为改革者的你将如何抉择？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287360/extras/819404857c6e157df6b947a154dea657.webp?t=1770501295\" width=263 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>视觉盛宴的近未来设计</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心融合野兽派、复古未来主义、侘寂风等设计风格，为每个区域打造独特而和谐的美术风格。配合专门定制的区域音乐，营造绝不重复的沉浸式体验。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287360/extras/0732c0012676eb012e579f803a83e9e9.poster.avif?t=1770501295\" width=1170 height=730 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287360/extras/0732c0012676eb012e579f803a83e9e9.webm?t=1770501295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287360/extras/0732c0012676eb012e579f803a83e9e9.mp4?t=1770501295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287360/extras/8b2b8cf7101a1902eb368d9f17d7c405.poster.avif?t=1770501295\" width=1170 height=730 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287360/extras/8b2b8cf7101a1902eb368d9f17d7c405.webm?t=1770501295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287360/extras/8b2b8cf7101a1902eb368d9f17d7c405.mp4?t=1770501295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深度刻画的角色群像</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看似逆来顺受的特种作战人员，神秘锋利却身不由己的基地指挥官——每个角色都隐藏着复杂的内心世界和引人入胜的过往故事，等待玩家深入探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富的世界探索体验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在自由探索中发现隐藏的人物对话、机密文件和军事档案。每个房间都藏着曾经发生的秘密，副官鱼鹰会为你收集的每份资料提供专业分析。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>策略与运气并行的卡牌战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80张独特卡牌，每张都有专属背景故事与技能组合。通过精彩的卡牌连招与基地人员进行情报交锋，在战斗中推进剧情发展。</p></li></ul>",
